=3D=3D Organization =3D=3D

The ISAO series is run by the International Association for Ontology an=
d its Applications (IAOA) [12] and is held jointly with FOIS every two =
years, typically in the week just before. ISAO 2023 is the 5th instance=
, after 2012/14/16/18 [13] and 5 years of an undesired gap, and is host=
ed by the University of Sherbrooke, Qu=C3=A9bec, Canada.

Thanks to local organization support in 2023 by
